Package: pmxcopula
Type: Package
Title: Copula Evaluation in Pharmacometric Anaylsis
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Laura B. Zwep, Yuchen Guo
Maintainer: Yuchen Guo <iguoyuchen@outlook.com>
Description: A comprehensive framework for copula model evaluation and virtual population simulation in pharmacometric analysis. 
    Provides functionality for calculating the marginal metrics (mean, median, standard deviation and percentiles) 
    and dependency metrics (correlation and overlap percentage) of the observed and simulated populations, generating 
    visual predictive check plots (qqplots and donutVPCs) of the copula model, applying subset simulation for specific 
    group of individuals, and more.
